divs: Sighting DetailsLooked like a star withe a short horn shaped trail under. Object was moving extremely slow to the NW. The trail under would suggest it would be moving up or East. It didnt look like a plane w the exhaust trailing it.
Object Flight Path: Hovering then path,Path with directional change
Summary: Looked likw a star with horn shaped trail comming from the bottom. Object gradually moving left--not forward or straight as the trail would suggest.
